# 🌾 Crop Yield Prediction Using Machine Learning

This project focuses on predicting crop yield based on various soil properties and environmental conditions using several machine learning algorithms. By integrating historical crop and soil data with advanced ML techniques, the system aims to support farmers and agricultural experts in making informed decisions to enhance productivity and sustainability.

